Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
set_pulse_clock_max_transition(25.10)    set_pulse_clock_max_transition(25.10)

Name
       set_pulse_clock_max_transition  -  Sets the maximum pulse clock transi-
       tion constraint on the specified pulse generator cells, pulse generator
       library cells, clocks, and/or current design

Syntax
       set_pulse_clock_max_transition

       <transition_limit>

       <object_list>

       [-transitive_fanout]

       [-rise]

       [-fall]

       Sets the maximum pulse clock transition  constraint  on  the  specified
       pulse  generator  cells,  pulse generator library cells, clocks, and/or
       current design.

Parameters
       -fall  Sets transition limit value for falling transition.

       <object_list>
              Specifies a list of objects - pulse generator cells, pulse  gen-
              erator library cells, clocks, or current design.

       -rise  Sets transition limit value for rising transition.

       <transition_limit>
              Specifies the transition limit value.

       -transitive_fanout
              Specifies the transition limit value for transitive fanout.

Examples
       The following example sets the max pulse clock transition constraint of
       0.1ns  on  the  input  pins  of  all  the  instances  of  the  lib cell
       PULSE_GEN_00:

       set_pulse_clock_max_transition 0.1 PULSE_GEN_00

       This constraint can be observed on the input pin  'A'  of  an  instance
       'pg_inst' of this lib cell using the following command:

       report_constraint pg_inst/A -drv_violation_type pulse_clock_max_transi-
       tion

       Fragmented output:

       Check type : pulse_clock_max_transition_rise

       ---------------------------

        ---------------------------------------------

        Pin Name Required Actual Slack

        ---------------------------------------------

        pg_inst/A 0.100 0.030 0.070

       Check type : pulse_clock_max_transition_fall

       ---------------------------

        ---------------------------------------------

        Pin Name Required Actual Slack

        ---------------------------------------------

        pg_inst/A 0.100 0.030 0.070

